ing: 2 (15 ounce) cans cannellini beans, rinsed and drained
3 cloves garlic, crushed or to taste
des: "An awesome alternative to the usual refried beans and tortilla chips.  Serve this dip with pita chips or veggie wheat crackers"
ins: In a food processor, combine the cannellini beans, cilantro, garlic, olive oil and lemon juice. Process until smooth, or to your desired consistency. Taste, and season with salt and pepper.
